{"tid":2109178,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子在警背後貼文宣 襲警罪成囚3周 官：輕判會加深警察困難","createTime":"2020-07-15T05:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T12:17:37.000Z","uid":203661,"like":6,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2da4ab3cf0062f3136a1b377a1874a372d51a0be","tid":2109178,"uid":203661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"男子在警背後貼文宣 襲警罪成囚3周 官：輕判會加深警察困難<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/38W7q0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38W7q0k&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu6QBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=52f59d67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38W7q0k</a><br />\n<br />\n被告今早被裁定罪成及判囚3周。裁判官指，被告觸碰時具敵對態度，構成毆打，又批評被告行為「像惡作劇一樣愚昧無比」，質疑被告為何不帶頭貼自己。裁判官又指，相關行為對警員極具羞辱性，強調法庭若輕判襲警者會加深警察執法的困難。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//裁判官陳慧敏指，被告在警員的背上張貼海報，所涉及的身體接觸已構成毆打。陳官不相信被告認為被張貼的男子身份不是警員，裁定被告襲警罪成。陳官考慮被告沒有悔意，亦無其他減刑因素，判被告即時監禁3星期。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係陳慧敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f6fd12f896a711878a2299059a393a03b1b843","tid":2109178,"uid":17506,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"裁判官陳慧敏指，被告在警員的背上張貼海報，所涉及的身體接觸已構成毆打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0804ffa6d9d088e08af19bfd363a29cffaca7754","tid":2109178,"uid":246118,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"貼張紙都襲警，仲廢過玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學生之間都會咁做啦，拉曬佢地"},{"pid":"6179962ff3948e281876160d1a34a1e7860d19ec","tid":2109178,"uid":362015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkg